该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - posts (read_write): Dict mapping post_id to {user_id, content, likes, timestamp}
  - users (read_write): Dict mapping user_id to {username, followers, following}
  - feed_cache (read_write): Dict mapping user_id to {feed, last_updated}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
